			<section class="pt2 pb4">
				<p class="f5 lh-copy measure-wide">
					<span class="leader f4">anonfiction</span> is a place for creative anonymous nonfiction.
				</p>
				<p class="f5 lh-copy measure-wide">
					Our mission is similar to <a href="https://www.thesunmagazine.org/submit#readers-write">The Sun’s Reader’s Write</a>, <a href="http://brevitymag.com">Brevity Magazine</a>, <a href="https://www.creativenonfiction.org">Creative Nonfiction Magazine</a>, <a href="http://www.100wordstory.org">100 Word Stories</a>, <a href="https://1966journal.org">1966 Journal</a>, <a href="https://concis.io">Concis</a>, <a href="http://proximitymagazine.org">Proximity Magazine</a>, <a href="https://spartanlit.com">Spartan Literature</a>, and <a href="http://threadliterary.com">Thread Literary</a>. However, unlike these magazines, we are devoted to publishing great <em>anonymous</em> nonfiction where great writing can take place despite the name of the person who writes it.
				</p>
			</section>
		</div>
		<div class="fl pa3 bg-white black-70 measure-narrow f3 pv4">
